    "name": "章节分隔页",
    "category": "opener",
    "description": "大编号章节分隔页（02 · Theme）",
    "htmlSnippet": "<section class=\"slide tc center\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:780px;margin:0 auto\">\n    <p class=\"kicker anim-fade-down\">Section · 02</p>\n    <h1 class=\"h1 anim-rise-in\" style=\"font-size:112px\">主题与 <span class=\"gradient-text\">Tokens</span></h1>\n    <div class=\"divider-accent\" style=\"margin:24px auto\"></div>\n    <p class=\"lede\" style=\"margin:0 auto\">换主题 = 换一份 CSS 变量。其他一切保持不变。</p>\n  </div>\n</section>"
